{"tid":108642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"冇朋友，連唔開心都唔知搵咩人傾訴好","createTime":"2017-02-05T11:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T14:30:30.000Z","uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be24c5699edbad36e915302ece28918f0bf3dbab","tid":108642,"uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b491facda70fcbe006066d99e95026ae91301f7","tid":108642,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"自己食囉 唔係點"},{"pid":"23aa4a88caf6c1f9cfdf172b7ad8bab68417e9bd","tid":108642,"uid":6294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"上黎講 我聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cb0b96bfae01798e184f7a1cd00acc5b055fd4","tid":108642,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"why unhappy?"},{"pid":"aba8de51ab1fa55c5b68d2b876a61b47d11bb3d5","tid":108642,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"一齊講下有咩唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fb43e6ddf1bf8a32ab33d890c5ea5688b44f4a","tid":108642,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe2ebbf3c9d5ecd9cdd9e457db8a9803d5c1b882","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"+1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好無助好迷茫 但都諗唔到可以搵邊個傾"},{"pid":"2a4c057e438904b85700def16807ce6efdf82cb9","tid":108642,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都係咁"},{"pid":"cf582973e8283bb946170cda0adf3e800cc37573","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262a6a0cae20c8f60d3b13bb0dcc276ac43701dd","tid":108642,"uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如我地一齊去蒲丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3561050e006248768e0e797286983a64345208f5","tid":108642,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個朋友都冇?你實會有幾個朋友既 但一時諗唔起佢地啫<br />\n點解要為左識朋友而去做自己唔鍾意做既事?返教會更加錯<br />\n我上年都係好似你咁 分左手 就開始日飲夜飲 生活亂哂 果段時間好似變左第二個人咁<br />\n分手既呢段時間真係好難渡過 但過左之後 一天都光哂 加油...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a6c0da2c7f3f795beca45b1b6d013ceb1180e4","tid":108642,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbb989aa2245e777ad66dd62e02b5f9e6a6623c6","tid":108642,"uid":3356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"出到黎做野 好難識到所謂既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54923f438af48eabf6b107ac98fff7f303db7870","tid":108642,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1c12fc948070844caf50f62cdaa755599e2ee27","tid":108642,"uid":54783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:56:59.000Z","msg":"我呢啲邊緣人都冇傾訴對象<br />\n咪又係一樣咁過"},{"pid":"9ef77aebb9ec84190e542d471ecceb6d6ea137c3","tid":108642,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecac10c4fbc890ac1e98c974a6167ce8ef75c285","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如我地一齊去蒲丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好阿樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b598ac6665e29c0e17e13b03a7d6851478e5a007","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個朋友都冇?你實會有幾個朋友既 但一時諗唔起佢地啫<br />\n點解要為左識朋友而去做自己唔鍾意做既事?返教會更加錯<br />\n我上年都係好似你咁 分左手 就開始日飲夜飲 生活亂哂 果段時間好似變左第二個人咁<br />\n分手既呢段時間真係好難渡過 但過左之後 一天都光哂 加油...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都叫有2 3個真心朋友 <br />\n有個去左外國生疏左<br />\n另外2個又有男朋友 而且好似講黎都唔會有咩唔同咁 以前有男朋友個陣好多時間都放係佢度 冇咩點經營友情 依加發現自己冇一個你當佢係第一 佢亦一樣既知己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b0f6b5158b26874b251f6010a09103d759fe87","tid":108642,"uid":43753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"定係一直都唔識點樣同人分享你的唔開心？其實一定有人會係你訴苦對象"},{"pid":"976b13c3d1e26d2b988e137f7b1a0fa2653325a8","tid":108642,"uid":27160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"就算有好多朋友  有d說話唔係話講就可以講"},{"pid":"0627e4690e2719a0a2c77247ae8242df0ff4c52b","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算有好多朋友  有d說話唔係話講就可以講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4fb2a8768fb990ddefab24f95fa76a8fe1e1ec","tid":108642,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:11:47.000Z","msg":"去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d373b864c31aada84c5305f4392dc286719f46","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定係一直都唔識點樣同人分享你的唔開心？其實一定有人會係你訴苦對象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時會覺得唔開心自己忍下 唔好影響到人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8121327676f2b25b100971656235d3ef392ae88","tid":108642,"uid":46330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算有好多朋友  有d說話唔係話講就可以講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea9d9565bc9d383b7ea430ce61163d0d8328ec9","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁"},{"pid":"d5b4d386659983a8962a7c4b0a16c8bccea20e79","tid":108642,"uid":35711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想返教會可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b947e30c9f9020900d816152ad709bcc0bb799","tid":108642,"uid":29350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"樓上兩個真心唔好為蒲而蒲<br />\n就算比你買到短暫嘅真空又點<br />\n到頭來你都唔會得到啲咩或者成長<br />\n無嘢係可以真係忘記到<br />\n倒不如作為一個開始比自己諗下<br />\n周圍體驗下，證明自己係可以識到朋友又好<br />\n想打發時間又好<br />\n其實成個世界仲有好多嘢等緊你架<br />\n<br />\n利申：長期灰暗人"},{"pid":"ff2aedf10e84333f3ef33003282e9e84d539f281","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想返教會可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興真心想搵個目標或者沉澱下自己"},{"pid":"219cee0e648b4d1f0203c7fbae00cd72c15d4bbd","tid":108642,"uid":35711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想返教會可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興真心想搵個目標或者沉澱下自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點聯絡<br />\n有興趣既話學唱歌都好、我果陣散開始學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c398337bb8943043111dde351eabe59035fbcc","tid":108642,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上兩個真心唔好為蒲而蒲<br />\n就算比你買到短暫嘅真空又點<br />\n到頭來你都唔會得到啲咩或者成長<br />\n無嘢係可以真係忘記到<br />\n倒不如作為一個開始比自己諗下<br />\n周圍體驗下，證明自己係可以識到朋友又好<br />\n想打發時間又好<br />\n其實成個世界仲有好多嘢等緊你架<br />\n<br />\n利申：長期灰暗人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗住揾d野學下等自己慢慢放底"},{"pid":"4080db8e6670cd5b65251890350fcf7306ed02fd","tid":108642,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想返教會可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興真心想搵個目標或者沉澱下自己</blockquote><br />\n我自己就去左做gym 由肥仔變做而家冇咁肥/會比人話幾句大隻<br />\n返緊工既可以瘋狂做野 讀緊書既就瘋狂溫書 時間好快會過 過左之後就會慢慢放低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606a63fdbcb74c4e25bf47dce35908d258058c54","tid":108642,"uid":24880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"可以留個tg一齊吹吓水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691e65d250471f47741d0f48430763c25a098c11","tid":108642,"uid":46330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去蒲無咩得著，唔去好過，你又唔係搵炮友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係好似唔知自己想做咩咁 想分下心 <br />\n可能遲d搵份parttime瘋狂返下咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下搵樣興趣搞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如踩單車..etc <br />\n唔少興趣都可以識到其他朋友 想自己玩又得 r fd一齊玩又得 會冇咁孤獨<br />\nbtw 你話廿歲未飲過野 我覺得唔需要特登去試<br />\n因為個個人鍾意既野都唔同  唔洗特登為左做而做<br />\n利申 我都未飲過 唔明有咩咁好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45696b9b49737b853ec05fdab73e7b140b17dd55","tid":108642,"uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定係一直都唔識點樣同人分享你的唔開心？其實一定有人會係你訴苦對象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你都講得啱，真係唔識點同人講我嘅唔開心，成日覺得講左人地都唔會明，又好怕煩到人，俾人hea應嘅話會仲唔開心"},{"pid":"42efb952f718df2acfa7a7f59f7576fdc376a28c","tid":108642,"uid":29350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想返教會可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興真心想搵個目標或者沉澱下自己</blockquote><br />\n我自己就去左做gym 由肥仔變做而家冇咁肥/會比人話幾句大隻<br />\n返緊工既可以瘋狂做野 讀緊書既就瘋狂溫書 時間好快會過 過左之後就會慢慢放低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，只不過係瘋狂做占同走堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b4a0b5cc0c60138e62bda8331bc944e139dad1","tid":108642,"uid":29350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>定係一直都唔識點樣同人分享你的唔開心？其實一定有人會係你訴苦對象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你都講得啱，真係唔識點同人講我嘅唔開心，成日覺得講左人地都唔會明，又好怕煩到人，俾人hea應嘅話會仲唔開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實不妨可以喺度講，無人會hea 你"},{"pid":"fe5554f6ba334e5f82fccaf50e83154cfa049232","tid":108642,"uid":75522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"要唔要telegram傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最近都有啲好戇鳩嘅感情事<br />\n戇鳩到同識嘅人講都覺得唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c14a6b2f3f50cedd549d429c2f6a89d608acf5","tid"