es/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同ex 散左已經半年 但見到佢ig snapchat post 同男仔遊山玩水都仲係好痛。。"},{"pid":"3126986bf86e1460717abab980233a6cc159b363","tid":108642,"uid":29350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都為情唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同ex 散左已經半年 但見到佢ig snapchat post 同男仔遊山玩水都仲係好痛。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打睇黎都好偒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc8941c67e1d4ed798f4940ffac185d1a432754","tid":108642,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"我鍾意左一個女仔四年幾<br />\n經歷過好多 但係始終都冇一齊到<br />\n自己仲要搞到朋友都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n然後身邊嘅朋友又一個一個咁離開我 背叛我<br />\n但係一個都幾熟嘅女仔 我擺曬我所有精力 情感比佢 <br />\n唔想再失去<br />\n但係有日佢好開心咁同我講佢有男朋友<br />\n我發覺原來我已經鍾意左佢<br />\n但係一切好似已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4190cf141ef02f0eec201d72c2fff0abbe5ca59d","tid":108642,"uid":68168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近同男朋友分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話我冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當下有諗過學下去蒲<br />\n利申已經二十 仲未試過去飲野<br />\n但又好似唔係自己想要咁 過唔到自己個關<br />\n唔係基督徒但係想返下教會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家唔好笑我 因為真係又無助又孤獨想搵d野做分下心 但又唔知自己可以做d咩去過渡呢段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都冇咩朋友，但男朋友反而鍾意我咁毒，做咩都係同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}